NOTICE

This repository includes original research and code related to the Coherence Quotient Q(t),
a spectral alignment diagnostic applied to turbulence and singularity detection in fluid systems.

This work is shared under the **Creative Commons Attribution–NonCommercial 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC 4.0)**.
To view the license, visit: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

